title: Victor Lewis on performing his composition with Woody Shaw
fulltitle: Victor Lewis on performing his composition with Woody Shaw
description:
WANT TO TRY IT YOURSELF? Get the leadsheet to "Seventh Avenue" on jazzleadsheets.com - https://jazzleadsheets.com/seventh-avenue.html

Drummer/composer Victor Lewis talks about his first years in New York and playing his composition "Seventh Avenue" with bandleader Woody Shaw for the first time.
